  "cooking_instructions": [
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Boil a kettle, then peel and finely chop (or grate) <strong>half</strong> your <strong>garlic</strong></p><p>Combine the <strong>chopped garlic </strong>and 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>sugar</strong> in a large bowl with your <strong>garam masala</strong>, <strong>lean</strong> <strong>beef mince </strong>and a pinch of <strong>salt</strong> and <strong>pepper </strong>(clean hands are the best way!)</p><p>Divide equally and shape into 6 meatballs per person</p>",
      "order": 1,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-1-1688112711912-x200.jpg",
