            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach </strong>then add to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over it so that it starts to wilt</p><p>Rinse the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> under <strong>cold running water</strong> until it's cool, then once cool, squeeze as much water out of the spinach as you can</p><p>Chop your <strong>green chilli</strong> in half</p><p>Crush the <strong>remaining garlic</strong> open by squashing with the side of a knife and discard the skin</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1688112715918-x200.jpg",
