        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Reboil half a kettle</p><p>Add the <strong>wilted spinach</strong> and <strong>half </strong>the <strong>green chilli</strong> (not a fan of spice? Just add a little!) to a <strong>food processor </strong>with the<strong> crushed garlic</strong>, <strong>ginger paste</strong>, <strong>curry powder </strong>and most of your <strong>coriander </strong>(save some for a garnish!)</p><p>Add a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a generous pinch of <strong>salt </strong>and <strong>pepper</strong></p><p>Blitz until smooth – this is your <strong>saag paste</strong></p>",
      "order": 5,
      "media": {
        "images": [
