            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>beef stock mix</strong> to the pan with 175ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[230ml]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[300ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Reduce the heat to medium and cook, covered, for 12-15 min or until the beef is cooked through (no pink meat!), stirring occasionally – this is your <strong>spicy saag gosht-style lean beef meatballs</strong></p><p>Slice the<strong> remaining green chilli</strong> into rounds</p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1688112733782-x200.jpg",
