            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>saag gosht-style lean beef meatballs </strong>with the<strong> cooked rice</strong> to the side</p><p>Drizzle over your <strong>natural yoghurt </strong>and dollop on your<strong> mango chutney</strong></p><p>Top with the<strong> remaining coriander </strong>and the <strong>chilli rounds </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!)</p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
